data.description: Dip your toes in beautiful Lake Norman. Just steps from the lake, this spacious 5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home boasts a deeded easily accessed boat slip on the desirable Winslow Bay neighborhood. This cul-de-sac home includes a Master on the main level, 4 bedrooms upstairs, and a basement w/ a large storage room. Walk into the 2nd story entrance leading into an open floor plan kitchen, family, dining, and sunroom. Space is not an issue! This family friendly community is walkable distance from many shopping centers and includes a park, tennis courts,  clubhouse, and pool. Park you camper, boat, or RV in Winslow Bay’s secure dry dock storage. Love life at the Lake!
